data.description: Move right in to this beautiful new construction home in immaculate condition and meticulously maintained. Bright, open and flexible floorplan. 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and approx 1880 sqft. Large eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, gas range, and pantry. Utility room with storage and washer/dryer hookups. Huge primary bedroom suite with walk-in closet, double sink vanity, soaking tub and separate shower. 2 additional spacious bedrooms. Relax in screened porch. Attached 2 car garage. Tankless water heater. MINIMUM CREDIT SCORE REQUIREMENT OF AT LEAST A 650. NON-SMOKING PREMISES. PETS CASE BY CASE WITH OWNER APPROVAL.
